{"id": "1244855792608477195", "channel_id": "1244855792608477195", "type": 0, "author_id": "597345991632486406", "author_name": "whimsical_starfish_19845", "author_bot": false, "content": "大家來驗驗血統吧。\n\n如果有什麼想要我補充的，請留言告訴我。\n\n※非理論確切結果，會有些許偏差，但大致應符合分布。", "timestamp": "2024-05-28T03:32:29.260000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-05-28T10:44:32.039000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 9}, {"emoji": "👍🏻", "emoji_id": null, "count": 3}], "attachments": [{"id": "1244855792952414238", "filename": "11.JPG", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 76334, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1244855792608477195/1244855792952414238/11.JPG?ex=69fb5f0d&is=69fa0d8d&hm=2c536fa52a97632fc9bf42b1e1e0f2b09e8d07b6c9a451a170a7fe31b48f0148&"}, {"id": "1244855793187164230", "filename": "22.JPG", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 83133, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1244855792608477195/1244855793187164230/22.JPG?ex=69fb5f0d&is=69fa0d8d&hm=1d60a1bbf91e3bf525850beb72f1c832a8353b67f616219693e9343685f48452&"}, {"id": "1244855793421910037", "filename": "31.JPG", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 118111, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1244855792608477195/1244855793421910037/31.JPG?ex=69fb5f0d&is=69fa0d8d&hm=5894b1cb1b9da304831499f619d79f922f3a592233dd0e8c2d508cb0e1845300&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1244855792608477195", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "限定角色、命輪抽卡出貨機率一覽表", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1174180524034637854"]}
{"id": "1244950580519108688", "channel_id": "1244950580519108688", "type": 0, "author_id": "597345991632486406", "author_name": "whimsical_starfish_19845", "author_bot": false, "content": "這次活動收益相當高，兌換物品也難以用金卷衡量，所以我只簡單算了能算的，如圖和表格。\n\n本次羊媽收益遠高於以往，推測是半周年的活動福利，我打算體力藥劑歐印了，各位可以斟酌考量。\n\n收益比較：第十關 > 第二到九關 >= 第一關\n\n缺印章的建議刷印章，其餘的就看自身情況考量，規劃當前擁有的資源去分配刷的關卡。", "timestamp": "2024-05-28T09:49:08.459000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 9}], "attachments": [{"id": "1244950580703793182", "filename": "6404.JPG", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 96243, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1244950580519108688/1244950580703793182/6404.JPG?ex=69fb0e94&is=69f9bd14&hm=6eb8afc699b8e286e8c257caa80532d15784779d55d489a32a92a322b50f220c&"}, {"id": "1244950580917440552", "filename": "d8355118599966d3.xlsx", "content_type": "application/vnd.openxmlformats-officedocument.spreadsheetml.sheet", "size": 32557, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1244950580519108688/1244950580917440552/d8355118599966d3.xlsx?ex=69fb0e94&is=69f9bd14&hm=c63c0c9953f14b68eb92a97dfb612993d0c972aab7350dfa3d968440b9cdbc6e&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1244950580519108688", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "羊媽活動收益", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1174180524034637854"]}
{"id": "1245006173363503177", "channel_id": "1245006173363503177", "type": 0, "author_id": "428893539561373726", "author_name": "chennnn328", "author_bot": false, "content": "此篇是利用每天零碎時間\n（從1.3下半拖到1.4 上半 今天終於完成了\n想到什麼就打進去備忘錄，字多多多多\n可能會有些語病或是說錯的地方\n\n偏基礎入門款\n並且文章內容可能不適用於每位玩家\n還請各位多多包容🙏\n\n\n至於傷害公式等等 這裡就不提太多了\n可以直接參考之前的文章\n我記得有一篇很詳細的說明了破鏈以及覺醒算法\n-------------------------------------------------\nhttps://youtu.be/FITl9sdOfO8\n只有文字解說感覺還差了一點\n就順便錄了今天的深潛\n有什麼造物就用什麼\n\n如果不想看boss之前的關卡\n可以直接跳到21分左右\n\n這局可惜的地方是臭腳沒有發揮到\n如果剛好有對上的話\n說不定可以讓回合數再更低一點\n\n造物都給狂氣相關的\n可以讓隊友們一直開大\n那我當然得好好利用\n（環拉回手真的太強大啦\n\n第六回合忘了清手牌\n少拿了一顆聖胎\n這算是蠻嚴重的失誤\n如果有吞到聖胎\n最後可以直接帶走", "timestamp": "2024-05-28T13:30:02.826000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-05-30T16:52:14.030000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 8}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [{"type": "video", "title": "5/30 深潛 希洛隊伍 全過程", "url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FITl9sdOfO8", "description": ""}], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1245006173363503177", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "給想要接觸希洛的守密人（5/30更新實戰影片", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1243105047332524043", "1174179734373019748"]}
